'''史波尼克高原''' {{IPAc-en|'|s|p|V|t|n|I|k|_|'|p|l|ei|n|@|m}}<ref group=note>Also {{IPAc-en|'|s|p|U|t|n|I|k}}, {{IPAc-en|'|p|l|ae|n|@|m}}</ref>是[[冥王星|冥王星]]上有著不規則溝槽切割的冰凍高原。這些溝槽大約{{convert|20|km|mi|abbr=on}}長，槽底可能有鏈狀的山或包含更為黯淡的物質<ref name=fp>{{cite web|last1=Gary|first1=Stuart|title=NASA'S New Horizons discovers frozen plains in the heart of Pluto's ‘Heart’|url=http://starstuffblog.tumblr.com/post/124564348008|accessdate=27 July 2015}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。史波尼克高原是心形的[[湯博區|湯博區]]西側，在表面上看似風吹出的條紋，是[[昇華|昇華]]的證據<ref name="TV-20150718">{{cite web |title=New high-resolution images show Pluto's 'icy, frozen plains' |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/7/17/8975623/nasa-new-horizons-pluto-flyby-mosaic-high-resolution |newspaper=TheVerge.com |date= |author= |accessdate=18 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226200726/http://www.theverge.com/2015/7/17/8975623/nasa-new-horizons-pluto-flyby-mosaic-high-resolution |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="JH-20150718">{{cite web |title=New Horizons |url=http://pluto.jhuapl.edu/News-Center/News-Article.php?page=20150717 |newspaper=Pluto.jhuapl.edu |date= |author= |accessdate=18 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120030420/http://pluto.jhuapl.edu/News-Center/News-Article.php?page=20150717 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20150717-video">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=NASA – Video (01:20) – Animated flyover of Pluto's icy mountain and plains |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydU-YrG_INk |date=17 July 2015 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] & [[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=18 July 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323031050/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydU-YrG_INk |dead-url=no }}</ref>。黑暗的條紋長數公里，都排列在相同的方向上<ref name=fp/>。高原也包含一些可能是昇華形成的小坑<ref name=fp/>。史波尼克高原的名稱是紀念歷史上第一顆成功發射的人造衛星，即[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的[[史普尼克1號|史普尼克1號]]而命名的。

多邊形的結構是對流的標記，推測是一層薄薄的水冰覆蓋著甲烷<ref name=Prent>{{cite web|last1=Prentice|first1=Andrew|title=Pluto revealed raises questions about its origins|url=http://www.abc.net.au/science/articles/2015/07/22/4278762.htm|website=ABC Science|accessdate=27 July 2015|date=22 July 2015|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926005224/http://www.abc.net.au/science/articles/2015/07/22/4278762.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

史波尼克高原的西南邊界與高聳出表面約{{convert|5200|ft|km|disp=flip|abbr=on}}的[[希拉蕊山|希拉蕊山]]接壤<ref name="SN-20150724">{{cite news |title=NASA’s New Horizons Discovers Exotic Ices on Pluto |url=http://www.sci-news.com/space/science-pluto-exotic-ices-hillary-montes-03060.html |date=24 July 2015 |work=SciNews.com |accessdate=25 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018063225/http://www.sci-news.com/space/science-pluto-exotic-ices-hillary-montes-03060.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，再往南是高出表面{{convert|11000|ft|km|disp=flip|abbr=on}}高的[[諾蓋山|諾蓋山]]<ref name="NASA-20150718">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=APOD: 2015 July 18 – Fly Over Pluto |url=http://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap150718.html |date=18 July 2015 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=27 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220033052/http://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap150718.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，這兩座山是以1953年5月29日第一位登上[[地球|地球]]最高峰[[珠穆朗瑪峰|珠穆朗瑪峰]]的[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]][[登山家|登山家]][[艾德蒙·希拉蕊|艾德蒙·希拉蕊]]爵士和[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]][[雪巴人|雪巴人]][[丹增諾蓋|丹增諾蓋]]命名<ref name="THT-20150719">{{cite web |last=Pokhrel |first=Rajan |title=Nepal’s mountaineering fraternity happy over Pluto mountains named after Tenzing Norgay Sherpa - Nepal's First Landmark In The Solar System |url=http://thehimalayantimes.com/latest/plutos-mountains-named-after-tenzing-norgay-sherpa |date=19 July 2015 |work=The Himalayan Times |accessdate=19 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813070429/http://thehimalayantimes.com/latest/plutos-mountains-named-after-tenzing-norgay-sherpa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。广阔的地區出人意料地命名为[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]的[[科列塔德達多斯丘|科列塔德達多斯丘]]，是以[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙人]]的[[科列塔德達多斯衛星|科列塔德達多斯衛星]]命名，以纪念第一顆在巴西發射進入[[太空|太空]]的人造衛星<ref>{{cite web | url = http://goasa.com.br/brasil-recebe-nomenclatura-em-plutao | title = Brasil recebe nomenclatura em Plutão | publisher = GOASA | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402133401/http://goasa.com.br/brasil-recebe-nomenclatura-em-plutao | archivedate = 2016-04-02 | accessdate = 2015-10-22 }}</ref>。
